</div>
<div>
<p>牛元翼<pc>，</pc>
<placeName>趙州</placeName>人<pc>。</pc>材果而謀<pc>。</pc>王承宗時倚其計為強雄<pc>，</pc>與傅良弼<measure quantity="2" unit="people">
